item.description: Join Barbara Moura as she welcome’s you to the Angel Healing Circle! Connect with others in the group as you join together and receive the healing energy of the Angels through positive, gently guided meditation and explore the “topic of the evening” through a group discussion (including a Q & A with Barbara) before closing out the session with a group Angel Card reading and an offering of thanks. The Angel Healing Circle will be held once a month so don’t miss out on your chance! Cost is $15 per person
